Gordon Lightfoot(1962) - Two Tones at the Village Corner (with Terry Whelan)

Someone else created this torrent.  I found it while searching.
Most of it downloaded in no time at all, but it took several days to
get the last pieces.  So, I've decided to upload it here in the hope
that it will see a little more TLC.  I'll seed it for awhile when I can.

I've been wanting this old album for years.  Unfortunately, this rip
is from a badly damaged source.  See the readme.txt file.  The
original uploader did what he could with what he had.  I'd love
to get ahold of original wav files for this album and do a full
restoration on it.  If anyone has a better rip, or torrent of one
please leave comments.
